gujarati.context:
That is a grand book most precious and very rare; 
in which the Lord's presence is manifest; 
manifest salvation, manifest worship, 
manifest commandment, manifest vision.

Here are the translations:

The second says "Moksha is reached after giving up, Prabhu explains Proksh is reached; 
Someone says Karma brings happiness, but many are unaware.

The dwelling is spiritual and that of the forest dweller; 
the dwelling is regal and that of the village, oh so divine;
the learning is for thieves, meat-eaters, and dark-souled; 
whoever stays there, their abode is dark.

For him who is moving away, your story will be sung beautifully; 
It will be understood by that which will be understood when; 
It will not be considered foolish that which will not be considered a fool there.
